question.title: How to merge multiple images into one in Java?
question.body:
I have multiple images (.jpg/.jpeg/.png) in form of Spring's MultiPartFile. I need to transform them into a single MultiPartFile with images places vertically - preferably PDF, but other image formats are also fine.

I have tried using iText and GroupDocs solutions, but they require paid licence for commercial use. Is there any free-to-use solution?
